      <title>使用BFG给git仓库瘦身</title>
      <link>https://leongravel.com/post/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8bfg%E7%BB%99git%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E7%98%A6%E8%BA%AB/</link>
